rpc.trackingDetails: HybridChain may automatically collect information regarding your computer hardware and software. This data can encompass details like your IP address, browser type, domain names, access times, and referring website addresses. This collection is in line with HybridChain's privacy policy and aims to optimize service provision and enhance user experience.https://docs.hybridchain.ai/privacy-policy
